# RoboLedger V5.2.22: Forensic Audit & Persistence Update

This update introduces critical features for session reliability, side-by-side forensic verification, and enhanced grid scannability.

## 📐 Layout Expansion (1166px) & Grid Fidelity
The "Island Stack" is expanded to **1166px**, and we've sharpened the structural scannability.

- [x] **Forced 1166px Width**: Standardized across Header, Action Bar, Switcher, and Grid.
- [x] **Sharpened Dividers**: Crisp `1px` separators added with optimized opacity (`30%` headers / `8%` body) for high-scannability without distraction.

## ⚡ Session Recovery (V5.2.20)
Never lose your work on an accidental refresh.
- [x] **In-Page Recovery Banner**: A sleek blue-bordered banner appears if previous data is detected.
- [x] **Continue vs Start New**: Choose to resume your flow or purge the ledger for a fresh start.

## 🕵️ Forensic Audit Drawer (V5.2.21)
Implement side-by-side verification to handle truncated or ambiguous descriptions.

- [x] **Integrated Sidebar**: Full-height drawer that compresses the main stage when active.
- [x] **Multi-Source Support**:
    - **PDF**: Embedded iframe viewer for high-fidelity source checking.
    - **CSV/Text**: Monospace scrollable preview for raw data verification.
- [x] **Contextual Sync**: Click any "Source" icon in the grid to immediately load the correct document fragment.

## ⚡ Performance & Logic
- [x] **Flicker-Free Switcher**: Filter-based performance (0ms latency).
- [x] **Adaptive Naming**: CHQ1, CHQ2 sequencing for intuitive navigation.
- [x] **Parser Polarity**: Deep-audit of Debit vs Credit logic (v5.2.19 fixed).

---
*RoboLedger V5: Forensic Integrity. Infinite Scale.*
- **COA Tagging**: Integrated the "All roads lead to COA" philosophy—transactions map to categories via high-fidelity tags rather than sub-ledgers.

## 🛠️ Parser Polarity Fix
Resolved a critical bug where all transactions were bucketed as "Credits". 
- **Debit Detection**: The engine now correctly identifies outgoings based on amount signs (`-`) and description keywords (`PURCHASE`, `WITHDRAWAL`).

---
**RoboLedger V5 is now functionally audited and performance-hardened.** 🚀
